name: Amazing Endless Rush - Jump, Run, Long jumper, rolling
name_original: Amazing Endless Rush - Jump, Run, Long jumper, rolling
description:
One day, I was woken up by the noise on the street. From my window, I saw a skillful jumper on the roofs, from building to building. Nobody can get near him. He is so fast...

He keep jumping and running endless, sometime make a long jump, and never collide with any obstacle!

Control the running superman in Amazing Endless Rush. How far can you run?

How to Play:
- Tap screen to jump, Tap two time to jump higher
- Do not touch any obstacle
